ent-OpenPlagueMenuAction = Open evolution menu
.desc = Opens the plague evolution menu.

ent-PlagueInfectAction = Infect
.desc = Infect the selected target with the plague.

plague-infect-action-desc = Infect the selected target with the plague. Costs { $cost } evolution points.

ent-PlagueForcedVomitAction = Vomiting fit
.desc = Force the infected target to vomit the contents of their stomach.

ent-PlagueAsthmaticAction = Asthmatic fit
.desc = Temporarily blocks the infected target's breathing.

ent-PlagueDizzinessAction = Dizziness
.desc = Cause dizziness in the infected target, confusing their sense of direction.

ent-PlagueSleepyAction = Sleep
.desc = Put the infected target into a brief sleep.

ent-PlagueInjuryAction = Open wounds
.desc = Make the infected target experience painful bleeding. Costs [color=crimson]2 evolution points[/color].

ent-PlagueCataractAction = Cataract
.desc = Damage the infected target's vision. Costs [color=crimson]2 evolution points[/color].

ent-PlagueHeartAttackAction = Heart attack
.desc = Kill the infected. Costs [color=crimson]3 evolution points[/color].

ent-PlagueImmunityBreakAction = Immunity break
.desc = Attempt to remove the target's immunity. Costs [color=crimson]2 evolution points[/color].

ent-PlagueSpawnSlimesAction = Slime swarm
.desc = Create plague slimes at the specified location. Costs [color=crimson]1 evolution point[/color].

ent-PlagueSpawnBugsAction = Bug swarm
.desc = Create a swarm of infectious bugs at the specified location. Costs [color=crimson]1 evolution point[/color].

ent-PlagueTpInfectedAction = Teleport to infected
.desc = Teleport to a random infected person.

ent-PlagueTpNotInfectedAction = Teleport to healthy
.desc = Teleport to a random healthy person.

ent-PlaguePolymorphMouseAction = Rat polymorph
.desc = Transform into a plague rat.

ent-PlagueRevertPolymorphMouseAction = True form
.desc = Return to the ghost form.